{title: Someone to love you}
{artist: Martin Delray}
{composer: Written by Ted Chalfant}

[C]She was sortin’ through some letters [F]he'd kept beneath their bed
And [G7]read the one he'd written her the week before he [C]left
It was the only way he [C7]knew to [F]make one last request
